01:24:27.855 --> 01:24:30.106
♪ By any means
just to get that cream ♪

01:24:30.190 --> 01:24:32.942
♪ It was hard, but I did it
Graduated to the big screen ♪

01:24:33.026 --> 01:24:36.112
♪ Now I'm on tour
